Corporate Events
in South Florida
Our private rooms are upscale, luxurious and OFFER A UNIQUE ENTERTAINMENT EXPERIENCE
Step into a world where business meets entertainment, where team building combines with karaoke magic, and where your corporate events turn into memorable, fun-filled experiences. We’re not just a karaoke venue; we’re your partner in creating exceptional corporate gatherings that your colleagues and clients will cherish.
Why Choose Us for Your Corporate Event?
Organizing a corporate party with the accompanying large group activities isn’t that easy. As such, when your company is looking for the best corporate event entertainment options, your managers are looking for something that offers the whole deal. So, what makes us one of the best corporate event venues in South Florida?
Here’s what we bring to the table:
Culinary Excellence:
Our diverse menu transcends the ordinary. Delight your taste buds with an array of culinary delights, from savory appetizers to gourmet entrées. We cater to diverse tastes, dietary requirements, and preferences to ensure everyone leaves with a smile.
Premium Beverage Selection:
Whether it's a celebratory toast or a casual sip, our bar is stocked with top-tier spirits, wines, and non-alcoholic options. Our mixologists are ready to craft signature cocktails that'll keep conversations flowing and spirits high. PlugIN is one of the best corporate event venues in South Florida, where guests never go thirsty!
State-of-the-Art Audiovisuals:
Impress your guests with our cutting-edge audio and visual systems. Make presentations and speeches shine, and when the workday is done, let loose with high-quality karaoke equipment that transforms your team into rock stars. Who said team-building activities for large groups can’t be like rock concerts? With us, your holiday corporate parties will never be the same!
Exceptional Service:
Our staff is dedicated to making your corporate holiday event seamless and stress-free. Friendly and professional, they'll cater to your every need, ensuring everyone feels like a VIP. Need tech support? We've got you covered. Craving a snack during brainstorming? Consider it done!
Turnkey Event Management for Your Corporate Party:
Planning a corporate event, holiday parties and large group activities has never been this effortless. We provide a dedicated event organizer who takes care of the logistics, so you can focus on your agenda. From coordinating presentations to managing catering, we handle it all. Your role? Just arrive and network!
Unique Team Building in Corporate Event Entertainment:
Karaoke isn't just about singing; it's about bonding and building camaraderie. Our themed team-building activities and icebreakers add a twist to traditional networking, fostering collaboration and connection among your team members. Still, we understand that not all of your colleagues will want to grab the mic for the performance of their lifetime. That’s why we offer private bars with delicious beverages and food. We understand that organizing large group activities isn’t a walk in the park, and that’s why we strive to offer something for everyone.
Versatile Spaces:
Our venue is adaptable to your corporate needs. Whether you're hosting a night in town with your colleagues or an annual celebration, we offer customizable spaces that can accommodate small gatherings or large corporate parties.
So, if you’re looking to elevate your corporate events, impress your clients, or reward your team, we’ve got the perfect setting for you. Come join us for a harmonious blend of business and pleasure where innovation meets entertainment.
Ready to transform your corporate holiday party into something extraordinary? Contact us today to start planning an unforgettable experience that will leave a lasting impression on your colleagues and clients alike.

Meeting / Conference Event
Take Your Meeting Further
Take Your Corporate Conference to the Next Level at PlugIN.
Make your next corporate conference extraordinary with PlugIN’s private room rental. Our venue is equipped with state-of-the-art technology and tailored services to meet all your needs.
Event Management by Our Team of Trusted Experts
At PlugIN, our team of trusted experts ensures every detail is meticulously planned and executed, regardless of the size or complexity of your event. From intimate team offsites to large conferences, we provide an unparalleled range of indoor and outdoor spaces that suit your specific requirements.
We Offer:
Innovative Tech and Tools:
Cutting-edge technology to facilitate seamless presentations and communications.
Expert Event Coordinators:
Dedicated professionals to help you plan and execute every aspect of your event.
Extraordinary Event Spaces:
Versatile and sophisticated rooms tailored to your needs.
Plenty of parking space:
FREE parking and Valet service.
Catering Services:
Enjoy a delicious, professionally served lunch to keep your attendees energized and focused.
Snack Area:
A well-stocked snack area offering a variety of snacks, coffee, and soft drinks throughout the conference.
Sustainability:
Commitment to sustainable practices in all our meeting experiences.
Our extensive portfolio ensures that you find the perfect venue for your event. Experience exceptional service, innovative solutions, and remarkable spaces designed to elevate your meetings.
For more information and planning tips, please click here and our Events Director will contact you.
Take your meeting further with PlugIN. Book your private room / venue today!

PlugIN Group
PlugIN was founded by Anat & Oded Golan who spent 4 years in Japan where they experienced the amazing Karaoke culture of East Asia. On a daily basis, people gather together to sing their favorite tunes and enjoy time spent with family, friends and co-workers. With the creation of PlugIN, the idea of a unique Westernized Karaoke experience was born!
Today, the PlugIN group owns and operates 7 Karaoke clubs (6 in Israel and 1 in the US).
Each venue includes private rooms of different sizes and design suited to different types of events ranging from intimate parties to large events accommodating 150 guests (some rooms have private bars), all equipped with state of the art audio and visual technology.

Franchise
PlugIN’s vision is to create a lively and unique entertainment culture that is meaningful to people of all ages and backgrounds who want to celebrate alongside friends, family and colleagues while enjoying music, delicious food and drinks. This vision is incorporated into the details of every corner of every one of our branches. In addition to our newest venues in Miami, the PlugIN chain currently operates 6 venues in cities across Israel. Plans are underway to continue expanding our footprint into major cities in the US and beyond.
​PlugIN’s culture is dynamic, fun and entrepreneurial. Our corporate management provides franchisee’s with the highest level of ongoing professional support, training, expertise and resources. If you’re interested in learning more about franchise or investment opportunities, please do not hesitate to reach out to our team at:
info@pluginkaraoke.com.

Event Space
in South Florida
Our private rooms are upscale, luxurious and OFFER A UNIQUE ENTERTAINMENT EXPERIENCE
Welcome to PlugIN: The Perfect Event Space for Private Events!
Get ready to turn your ordinary gathering into an extraordinary experience! If you are looking to rent a venue for a party, you’ve come to the right place! We’re not just your average karaoke joint – we’re your go-to destination for unforgettable private events packed with fun, fantastic food, and fabulous friends.
Why Choose PlugIN As Your Private Party Venue?
We are the go-to private event space in South Florida. From birthday parties for kids and bat/bar mitzvahs to bachelor parties, we offer way more than simple private karaoke: We offer the full deal when you are looking to rent a venue for a party. So what makes us the best private event space in South Florida?
Check out everything that comes with our private party venue:
Delicious Dining Options:
Our menu isn't just a sidekick to the main act; it's a star in its own right! Savor a wide range of mouthwatering dishes that cater to every palate. From delectable appetizers to gourmet burgers, we've got it all covered. And don't forget the desserts that'll make your taste buds sing!
Thirst-Quenching Drinks:
We take mixology to the next level. Our expert bartenders craft cocktails that are nothing short of magic alongside an impressive selection of beers, wines, and non-alcoholic options. Raise your glass and toast to a night to remember!
High-Tech Audiovisuals:
Our top-notch audio and visual systems will make your karaoke performances shine like a superstar's concert. Feel the energy as you belt out your favorite tunes with professional-grade equipment that ensures you sound your absolute best.
Friendly Staff:
Our team is here to make your event a breeze. Our staff isn't just helpful; they're like your karaoke-loving friends who ensure your experience is as smooth as butter. Need a song suggestion? We've got you covered. Want another round of drinks? Consider it done! With us, your holiday parties will never be the same!
State-of-the-art Private Party Venues:
We offer the best private event spaces in all of South Florida, FACT. From smaller venues to massive spaces capable of catering to the needs of a crowd of around 150 people, PlugIN offers the ultimate party experience with private bars, and the best foods and drinks.
Turnkey Solutions:
Planning a private event has never been this easy. When you book with us, you get a dedicated event organizer who will handle all the nitty-gritty details. From setting up your customized playlist to coordinating food and drink orders, we've got it all under control. All you need to do is show up and enjoy the party! Organizing a holiday party has never been easier!
Party Like You’ve Never Partied Before
So, whether you’re celebrating a birthday, hosting a corporate gathering, or just craving a night of singing your heart out with friends, we’ve got the perfect space for you. Come on over, take the stage, and let the good times roll.
Ready to make your private event or holiday party legendary? Contact us now to start planning an unforgettable experience that’ll have your guests raving about it for years to come!
